item.title: Planes!
item.dc:creator: @Cole1497 Cole1497
item.description:
@Cole1497 wrote:

Flying mods would be stupid. This is supposed to be close to single player, with the inclusion of residence and login system to prevent griefers and hackers. If we add planes, that will not only encourage griefers, but ruin the point of survival altogether. We might as well enable spawning for free build “to work on our art” or whatever.
